fields.name: Air Max 95 OG Neon
fields.description: The 2020 Nike Air Max 95 retro is as OG as its 1995 debut. The original design was based on the human body, specifically the ribcage. Keeping up with the ribcage inspiration, the upper features its quintessential ripple makeup, stacking suede in a gradient pattern. Pops of neon green appear throughout from the air bubbles to the miniature Swoosh logo on the ankle. Reflective detailing is featured on the heel and tongue, making this a true OG return.

fields.name: Air Max 95 OG Crystal Blue
fields.description: The Nike Air Max 95 OG Crystal Blue showcases a gradient of gray on the paneled upper as hits of blue on the tongue, lancelets, and lining work together to decorate Sergio Lozano's signature look. Meanwhile, the midsole is designed in black and hosts blue-tinted Air pockets, and the outsole unit reveals n AM95 PSI. The sneaker showcases white mesh on most parts, including the outsole, Max Air sole unit, eyelets, Swoosh logos, and blue accents on the tongue lining. Moreover, the rubber outsole imitates the black midsole to round out the significant features of the sneaker.

fields.name: Air Max 95 OG Black Anthracite
fields.description: The upper of the OG Black Anthracite Nike Air Max 95 is crafted from a blend of premium leather, mesh, and synthetic materials. The heel includes a visible Air Max unit to provide optimal cushioning for high-impact activities. The shoe also boasts Nike branding, with the Swoosh logo on the lateral and medial sides and the Nike Air logo on the heel. Additionally, the shoe has reflective detailing throughout. The outsole is made of rubber for enhanced grip.

fields.name: Air Max 95 OG Solar Red
fields.description: One of the most popular Air Max silhouettes of all time, the Nike Air Max 95 is back in an OG colorway. Last releasing in 2011, the Solar Red colorway is back in original fashion. This pair utilizes a white, solar red, granite, and dust color palette. The unique Air Max 95 model, designed by Sergio Lozano, draws inspiration from the human-anatomy. This pair released for $160 in July 2018.

fields.name: Air Max 95 OG Fresh Mint
fields.description: Get fresher than a mint and cop the Air Max 95 OG Fresh Mint. This AM 95 comes with a grey upper plus white and mint accents, mint Nike 'Swoosh', black midsole, and a black sole. These sneakers released in May 2019 and retailed for $160. Grab these fresh kicks on StockX now.
